<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="Portfolio and professional services for Sarah Robin, a dev and designer based out of Northern CA">
    <meta name="author" content="Sarah Robin">

    <title>Sarah Robin | Design & Engineering</title>
    <%# <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous"> %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/css/app.css") %>">
    <%# <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ubuntu:400,700" rel="stylesheet"> %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Crimson+Text:400,400i,600,600i,700,700i|Oswald:200,300,400,500,600,700|Fira+Sans:300,400,500" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
  </head>

  <body>
        
    <div class="page__home">
      <section class="home__splash">
        <div class="splash__title">
          <h1 class="title__logotype display-sans">
            sarah robin
          </h1>

          <h2 class="title__subtitle">
            Design &amp; Engineering
          </h2>
        </div>

        <ul class="splash__social-links">
          <li class="social-links__link">
            <a target="_blank">Github</a>
          </li>

          <li class="social-links__link">
            <a target="_blank">Dribbble</a>
          </li>

          <li class="social-links__link">
            <a target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
          </li>

          <li class="social-links__link">
            <a target="_blank">Twitter</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="home__about">
        <div class="column about__details">
          <img class="details__pic" src="http://placehold.it/200x200">
        </div>

        <div class="column about__bio">
          <p>
            <span>Hi! I'm a designer and engineer</span> who builds web and mobile applications.
            My passion is for finding and implementing reliable solutions for everyday 
            problems that people face.
          </p>

          <p>
            For <strong>development</strong>, I commonly work w/ a varied Javascript stack for rapid 
            prototyping and full-stack MVP projects, though I enjoy Ruby for side
            projects and dabbling in Python.
          </p>

          <p>
            For <strong>design</strong>, I prefer an empathetic and people-centered approach to 
            product development and user experience, that works towards responsible 
            growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <script src="<%= Routes.static_path(@conn, "/js/app.js") %>"></script>
  </body>
</html>